    <briefdescription>
<para>Represents a 4-dimensional vector of the generic type &lt;T&gt;. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The `vec4` struct provides a lightweight and efficient way to handle 4D vector mathematics for the numeric types float, int, double. For convenient access, the shorthands `vec4f`, `vec4d` and `vec4i` are available.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>T</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The numeric type of the vector components. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
